{"tid":1748141,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國人旅日不受歡迎　習近平：源於日本人偏見　日方負主要責任","createTime":"2019-11-23T13:52:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T13:52:59.000Z","uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3adc444bea2e848d02577c542f009b662b9b0827","tid":1748141,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T13:52:59.000Z","msg":"日本多年來都是中國人的旅遊熱點，但中國遊客亦不時於當地與日本人發生不愉快事情。根據彭博報道，中國國家主席習近平今日在北京出席彭博社新經濟論壇，回應前日本外相川口順子（Yoriko Kawaguchi）一個問題時，將中國人在日本低人氣的問題，歸咎於日本人的偏見與成見。他認為這主要是日方的責任，但同意中國亦需要做一些事情修補。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述習近平於論壇上表示，中國人對日本人持較正面的看法，顯示中國向正確的方向發展，亦指中國沒有散播仇日主義，反而鼓勵人民到日本旅遊。他稱，中日兩國在整個歷史上總體是友好的，承認曾有一段短暫令人不愉快的歷史，亦令中國人民的心中留下深刻的印象，但任何衝突不會令任何一方受益。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA%E6%97%85%E6%97%A5%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%97%E6%AD%A1%E8%BF%8E-%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3-%E6%BA%90%E6%96%BC%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E4%BA%BA%E5%81%8F%E8%A6%8B-%E6%97%A5%E6%96%B9%E8%B2%A0%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E8%B2%AC%E4%BB%BB/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2597%2585%25E6%2597%25A5%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%258F%2597%25E6%25AD%25A1%25E8%25BF%258E-%25E7%25BF%2592%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%25B9%25B3-%25E6%25BA%2590%25E6%2596%25BC%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2581%258F%25E8%25A6%258B-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%2596%25B9%25E8%25B2%25A0%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%25B2%25AC%25E4%25BB%25BB%2F&d=z%2Bfr9BvhH3rd6UlN4MOb%2FnqjnVJZrvj6qhhAu%2BA3ahw%3D&h=a0bedccf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%2597%2585%25E6%2597%25A5%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%258F%2597%25E6%25AD%25A1%25E8%25BF%258E-%25E7%25BF%2592%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%25B9%25B3-%25E6%25BA%2590%25E6%2596%25BC%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2581%258F%25E8%25A6%258B-%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%2596%25B9%25E8%25B2%25A0%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E8%25A6%2581%25E8%25B2%25AC%25E4%25BB%25BB%2F&h=0895736c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA%E6%97%85%E6%97%A5%E4%B8%8D%E5%8F%97%E6%AD%A1%E8%BF%8E-%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3-%E6%BA%90%E6%96%BC%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E4%BA%BA%E5%81%8F%E8%A6%8B-%E6%97%A5%E6%96%B9%E8%B2%A0%E4%B8%BB%E8%A6%81%E8%B2%AC%E4%BB%BB/</a>"}]}